title: skogai.sh
content: The primary incantation of the SkogAI system, skogai.sh stands as the most-used spell in the registry. With 35 invocations between September 19-20, 2025, and active maintenance (last edited September 19), this script serves as a central command interface for the SkogAI ecosystem.
summary: The most frequently invoked script in the SkogAI ecosystem with 35 executions

relationships.description: skogai.sh is the primary script of the SkogAI ecosystem, serving as the most frequently invoked entry point to the central AI entity's capabilities.
